MyBroadband’s promotional newsletter platform makes it easy to reach 180,000 South African IT decision-makers with a targeted message. The newsletter platform allows companies to send their email message, which is customised with their styling and branding, to all subscribers. The subscribers include CEOs, CTOs, CIOs, and IT managers across all industries, including IT, telecoms, finance, and the government. It is a highly effective way for companies to promote their products, get webinar signups, and generate interest in their services among this influential audience. Over the past year, there has been a spike in MyBroadband’s promotional newsletters thanks to the excellent response rate and return on investment. Companies in all industries are now using MyBroadband’s promotional newsletter platform, including mobile operators, ISPs, IT providers, banks, and insurance companies. For more information about MyBroadband’s promotional newsletters, visit MyBroadband’s advertising page.